ST - Start tape recording

Syntax:   ST=<direction>,<speed>,<record status>
Response: ST/<direction>,<speed>,<record status>

Settable parameters:
<direction>: FOR to move tape forward, REV to move in reverse. No
             default. When the tape is stopped, this parameter is
             reported as REV.
<speed>: 3, 7, 15, 30, 60, 120, 240 IPS. When the tape is stopped,
         this parameter is reported as 0.
<record status>: ON to record; OFF to disable recording. Default
                 is ON.

Monitor-only parameters: none

      Comments: The tape is started moving. Record is enabled
unless the third parameter is specified as OFF. Reproduce mode is
not changed.
